  <h2><%= link_to "Techmet", "", target: "_blank" %><span>IIT Madras</span></h2>
  <hr>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-2 div-image">
        <%= image_tag("helmet.png", class: "image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <p>Techmet is a safety helmet, which in case of serious accident, will instantly send the location coordinates through SMS to national police service and ambulance.<br/><br/>Patent Application Number - 69/CHE/2011<br/>Title: ‘A Novel E-Headgear to prevent and warn against drunken driving in two wheelers’<br/><br/>Team Duos: Mohit Mittal and Rajan<br/><br/><a href="http://www.rediff.com/getahead/report/a-mobike-helmet-that-sends-sos-alerts/20091006.htm">Rediff</a> | <a href="http://www.deccanherald.com/content/28067/iit-prodigies-give-birth-techmet.html">Deccan Herald</a> | <a href="http://mobiletoi.timesofindia.com/mobile.aspx?article=yes&pageid=4&sectid=edid=&edlabel=TOICH&mydateHid=30-09-2009&pubname=Times+of+India+-+Chennai&edname=&articleid=Ar00404&publabel=TOI">Times of India</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2><%= link_to "Robocon", "", target: "_blank" %><span>IIT Madras</span></h2>
  <hr>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-2 div-image">
        <%= image_tag("robocon.png", class: "image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <p>Robocon is an international autonomous robotics competition for Asia-Pacific Region. Among 58 participating colleges across India, IIT Madras was declared as National Champion and was awarded with ‘Best Design Award’ for one of its robot in 2009. We represented India at an international level held at Tokyo, Japan, along with 21 other participating countries.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GYC5KA87D9M">ABU Robocon 2009 Problem Statement</a><br/><br/></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2><%= link_to "Want to fly", "https://www.facebook.com/cfiiitm", target: "_blank" %><span>IIT Madras</span></h2>
  <hr>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-2 div-image">
        <%= image_tag("wanttofly.png", class: "image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <p>This was one of the spirit of engineering projects in IIT Madras. First time ever in IIT Madras, we built an automated Unmanned Aerial Vehicle (wingspan – 2.6 meters and weight – 10Kgs) designed to go through pre-defined coordinates given by GPS technology.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

