  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-2 div-image">
        <%= image_tag("shaastra.png", class: "image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <p><a href="http://shaastra.org/" target="_blank">Shaastra</a> is a student organized and ISO certified annual technical festival of IIT Madras. We, three of us, were heading a team of 199 coordinators and 202 volunteers with over 67 diverse events catering to the interests of almost all students with various backgrounds across the country</p>
